is no life, without death there is no regeneration<lb/>
&amp; <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">heaped</del> Heat, Light &amp; those powers which depend<lb/>
upon repulsive energies are no less essential than<lb/>
attractions or gravitation in producing beauty<lb/>
and order of the system of the universe,<lb/>
