which appeared partly wild &amp; partly culti=<lb/>
=vated: there were fewer woods &amp; morasses<lb/>
than in the scene I had just before seen.<lb/>
I saw men who were covered with the skins<lb/>
of animals &amp; who were driving <del xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0"
                 rend="strikethrough">animals</del>
